description: For sale: $225,000. 10 acre parcel on the corner of Highways 22 & 25 in Angora. 3+/- acres with 2 bedroom/1 bathroom house, the "Principal's Residence". Home is in great shape and has detached garage. 7+/- acres features the "Alango School & Teacherage". School is on the National Registry of Historic Places and has had multiple renovations and restorations to keep it's old charm. School features all you would expect - classroom,s bathrooms, library, gym, locker rooms, cafeteria, etc. As well as upper level "teacherage" - 3 bedroom/1 bathroom living quarters. This property could be used for many of things, bring your ideas or continue the tradition of the Alango School. So much character in the buildings!
